 BLACKPINK 的 Jennie 发行新单曲《You & Me》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-you-and-me-3508828?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=blackpink-jennie-you-and-mePuah Ziwei Fri, 06 Oct 2023 04:00:20 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3508828 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="blackpink 珍妮 你和我" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手此前曾在女子组合“Born Pink”巡演中演唱过这首歌</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-you-and-me-3508828">BLACKPINK 的 Jennie 发布新单曲“You &amp; Me”</a>后首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="blackpink 珍妮 你和我" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jennie-blackpink-you-and-me-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennie">Jennie</a>发行了她的新个人单曲《You &amp; Me》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/song-of-the-bandits-heres-what-to-watch-next-3508367">《强盗之歌》完成了吗？这是接下来要看的内容</a></strong></li></ul><p>Jennie于周三（10月4日）通过BLACKPINK官方Instagram宣布了这首新歌。 《You &amp; Me》被宣传为“特别单曲”，并于 2022 年 10 月在韩国首尔 KSPO 巨蛋<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-kick-off-world-tour-in-seoul-jennie-performs-unreleased-solo-song-footage-setlist-3329584">举行的 BLACKPINK “Born Pink”世界巡演</a>开幕音乐会上首次亮相。</p><p>这首歌的混音版本还出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/blackpink-coachella-2023-k-pop-superstars-headline-set-3431069">2023 年 Coachella 音乐节女团主唱节目</a>中，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/blackpink-live-london-bst-hyde-park-3464046">2023 年 7 月在 BST 海德公园的演出</a>中。</p><p>这首歌的视频一开始，珍妮的嘴以黑白投影在巨大的圆形屏幕上，她唱着这首歌的开场白。然后镜头切到明星和一群舞者在浪漫的曲目中表演优雅的舞蹈。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="JENNIE - “你和我”舞蹈表演视频" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eQNHDV7lKgE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “<em>世界上没有什么能让我感受到你所做的事情，你所做的事情</em>，”她唱道。 “<em>我爱你和我，在月光下跳舞/没有人能看到，今晚只有你和我</em>。”这首歌曲还收录了 Jennie 的“You &amp; Me”表演的 Coachella 版本中的说唱诗句。</p><p>据<a href="https://twitter.com/Kpop_Herald/status/1709421137539846211"><em>《K-pop Herald》</em></a>报道，YG 娱乐公司在有关发行《You &amp; Me》的新闻稿中表示，“我们希望这首歌成为一份特别的礼物，让歌迷们记住他们在《Born Pink》巡演中的回忆”。</p><p> 《You &amp; Me》是 Jennie 自 2018 年以《Solo》个人出道以来的首张专辑。今年早些时候，这位歌手还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>和 Lily-Rose Depp 一起出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-and-blackpinks-jennie-share-new-song-from-the-idol-one-of-the-girls-3459947">“One of the Girls”</a>中，作为 HBO<em>电视剧《偶像》</em>原声带的一部分。</p><p> Jennie 的《You &amp; Me》发行之际<a href="https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2023/09/732_359832.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">，韩国媒体报道</a>称 BLACKPINK 的部分成员可能不会与 YG Entertainment 续约。然而，韩国流行音乐机构坚称讨论仍在继续，有关该团体合同的任何内容都尚未得到证实。</p><p>上个月，Jennie 在接受<em>《Harper&#39;s Bazaar》韩国版</em>采访时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-working-on-new-solo-music-3502428">开玩笑说她正在创作新的、“独特”的独奏音乐</a>。与此同时，乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">Lisa</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-lisa-joins-spotify-billions-club-playlist-money-3504160">凭借一首个人歌曲成为第一个在 Spotify 上达到 10 亿次播放量的韩国流行偶像</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-you-and-me-3508828">BLACKPINK 的 Jennie 发布新单曲“You &amp; Me”</a>后首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
